channel.title: Error at serverstatus -.-
channel.description:
Well, I have 2 errors actually :(
I have posted my server over and over again and I'm sick of it. Serverstatus almost always says SERVER OFFLINE once I refresh the page and it's instantly at 50%.
Now it won't even let me post the server for the 14th time (I keep track lol) It says you can only post one server. I have never changed my IP before and it always would work though.
If you know how to fix either one of these please post!
